     * file format set to <code> FTP.NON_PRINT_TEXT_FORMAT </code>,
     * the file structure set to <code> FTP.FILE_STRUCTURE </code>, and
     * the transfer mode set to <code> FTP.STREAM_TRANSFER_MODE </code>.
     ***/
